District Rankings

Source: R/tba_interfaceR.r
district_rankings.Rd

Reads district rankings

Usage

district_rankings(
  district_key,
  separate_events = FALSE,
  event_breakdown = FALSE
)

Arguments

district_key

(character) TBA legal district key

separate_events

(bool) split up team performance across each event?

event_breakdown

(bool) breakdown event performance?

Value

tidy tibble of event rankings

Author

Gabriel Krotkov

Examples

district_rankings("2016mar", separate_events = TRUE, event_breakdown = TRUE)
